                    </div>
                    <span>The whining drunk shows his true colors.  Should have been off the air at least 10 years before they finally showed him the door.  What a low-life ... if you're broke, it's your fault.  And, if you lost the Masters vs. Arnie, it's because you didn't play well enough to win.</span>
                  
              
